# 03 â€” Key Metrics and KPIs

## Core Metrics
| Metric | Formula | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| **CTR** (Click Through Rate) | clicks / impressions | Engagement level |
| **CVR** (Conversion Rate) | conversions / clicks | Effectiveness of clicks |
| **CPC** (Cost Per Click) | spend / clicks | Average cost per click |
| **CPA** (Cost Per Acquisition) | spend / conversions | Average cost per conversion |
| **CPM** (Cost Per Mille) | (spend / impressions) * 1000 | Cost per 1000 impressions |
| **ROI** (Return on Investment) | (revenue - spend) / spend | Profitability |
| **ROAS** (Return on Ad Spend) | revenue / spend | Revenue efficiency |

## Financial Metrics
- **Revenue** = total income from conversions
- **Spend** = total amount invested in ads
- **Profit** = revenue - spend
- **CAC** (Customer Acquisition Cost) = total spend / new customers
- **LTV** (Lifetime Value) = average revenue generated per customer

## KPI Usage
- **CTR & CVR:** measure engagement and efficiency
- **CPC & CPA:** measure cost efficiency
- **ROI & ROAS:** measure profitability
- **CPM:** compare awareness campaigns
